      <description>&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;In this episode Stephane, Pierig and I discuss the updates to AWS and GCP since our last show.&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://stephanefrechette.dev/images/datascape_july.jpeg&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;datascape&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Link to episode:&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://soundcloud.com/datascapepodcast/episode-43-july-2020-cloud-update-discussion&#34;  class=&#34;external-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Episode 43 - July 2020 Cloud Updates&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
